imdb.plot outline: Everyone faces challenges in life. Truly successful people find a way to stare down challenges, rise above obstacles, and not let temporary failures prevent them from fulfilling their dreams. MoxieTalk seeks out courageous men and women in all fields, so they can help educate and inspire future leaders and innovators.
